#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Formats"
msgstr "Formati datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unless you choose to use a <link linkend=\"details.database\">relational "
"database</link>, &kmymoney; will store all your financial information in a "
"file. Most commonly, the file name will end in <filename class=\"extension"
"\">.kmy</filename>. Also, when you launch &kmymoney;, unless you use a <link "
"linkend=\"firsttime.launch\">command line option</link> that tells it not to "
"do so, it will open the last file it had open. However, it is important to "
"know that there is actually more than one type of file &kmymoney; can use to "
"hold your financial data."
msgstr ""
"Razen če se odločite za uporabo <link linkend=\"details.database"
"\">relacijske zbirke podatkov</link>, &kmymoney; bo vse vaše finančne "
"podatke shranil v datoteko. Najpogosteje se ime datoteke konča z <filename "
"class=\"extension\">.kmy</filename>. Ko zaženete &kmymoney;, razen če "
"uporabite <link linkend=\"firsttime.launch\">možnost ukazne vrstice</link>, "
"ki mu pove, naj tega ne stori, bo odprl zadnjo datoteko, ki jo je odprl. "
"Vendar je pomembno vedeti, da dejansko obstaja več kot ena vrsta datoteke "
"&kmymoney; lahko uporabite za shranjevanje vaših finančnih podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter describes the file formats in which &kmymoney; can store its "
"data in permanent form. It also discusses backing up your data."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju so opisani formati datotek, v katerih &kmymoney; lahko hrani "
"svoje podatke v trajni obliki. Obravnava tudi varnostno kopiranje vaših "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data File formats"
msgstr "Formati podatkovnih datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In general, &kmymoney; stores its information in form of an &XML; document. "
"Depending on the actual format, which is set in &kmymoney;'s configuration, "
"this &XML; document will be written: <itemizedlist> <listitem><para>as a "
"plain text file, encoded in UTF-8,</para></listitem> <listitem><para>as a "
"compressed file, using GZIP compression,</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>as an encrypted file, using GPG encryption, or</para></"
"listitem> <listitem> <para> as an anonymous plain text file, encoded in "
"UTF-8 but with all your personal data scrambled. </para> </listitem> </"
"itemizedlist> Each of these is described in more detail in the following "
"sections."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno &kmymoney; shrani svoje podatke v obliki &XML; dokumenta. Odvisno "
"od dejanskega formata, ki je nastavljen v konfiguraciji &kmymoney;, ta &XML; "
"dokument bo zapisan: <itemizedlist> <listitem><para>kot datoteka z navadnim "
"besedilom, kodirana v UTF-8,</para></listitem> <listitem><para>kot stisnjena "
"datoteka z uporabo stiskanja GZIP,</para></listitem> <listitem><para>kot "
"šifrirana datoteka z uporabo šifriranja GPG ali</para></listitem> <listitem> "
"<para>kot anonimno golo besedilno datoteko, kodirano v UTF-8, vendar z vsemi "
"vašimi osebnimi podatki premetanimi. </para> </listitem> </itemizedlist> "
"Vsak od teh je podrobneje opisan v naslednjih razdelkih."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plain text file"
msgstr "Navadna besedilna datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the most space consuming format supported, as no compression is "
"performed. It is not intended for normal use, and is provided to support "
"debugging purposes and the capability to modify the file manually. If you "
"end a filename in <filename class=\"extension\">.xml</filename>, the file "
"will be stored in this format."
msgstr ""
"To je podprt format, ki porabi največ prostora, saj se ne izvaja stiskanje. "
"Ni namenjen običajni uporabi in je na voljo za podporo namenom odpravljanja "
"napak in zmožnosti ročnega spreminjanja datoteke. Če ime datoteke končate v "
"<filename class=\"extension\">.xml</filename>, bo datoteka shranjena v tem "
"formatu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Manual modification of the file is not recommended to the normal user, and "
"should only be performed if the internal working of &kmymoney; is fully "
"understood or if instructions from the developers tell you what to do. Don't "
"blame the &kmymoney; developers if you damage or destroy your data: You have "
"been warned!"
msgstr ""
"Ročno spreminjanje datoteke običajnemu uporabniku ni priporočljivo in ga je "
"treba izvesti le, če notranje delovanje &kmymoney; v celoti razumete ali če "
"vam navodila razvijalcev povedo, kaj morate storiti. Ne krivite razvijalcev "
"&kmymoney;, če poškodujete ali uničite svoje podatke: Bili ste opozorjeni!"

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "GZIP-compressed file"
msgstr "Stisnjena datoteka GZIP"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the normal format used by &kmymoney; when you store a file with the "
"extension <filename class=\"extension\">.kmy</filename>."
msgstr ""
"To je običajni format, ki ga uporablja &kmymoney; ko shranite datoteko s "
"pripono <filename class=\"extension\">.kmy</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <link linkend=\"details.formats.encrypted\">encryption</link> has been "
"selected in the configuration, the file will be stored encrypted, as "
"described in the next section."
msgstr ""
"Če ste v konfiguraciji izbrali <link linkend=\"details.formats.encrypted"
"\">šifriranje</link>, bo datoteka shranjena šifrirano, kot je opisano v "
"naslednjem razdelku."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to look at the contents of a GZIP compressed file, rename it to "
"a filename ending in <filename class=\"extension\">.gz</filename> (&eg;, "
"rename <filename>myfinances.kmy</filename> to <filename>myfinances.kmy.gz</"
"filename>), then use <command>gunzip</command> to uncompress the file and "
"look at it. You don't have to compress it before loading it into &kmymoney; "
"the next time, because &kmymoney; can read the uncompressed data as well. "
"Nevertheless, if you save it thereafter, it will be saved compressed again. "
"Use the <link linkend=\"details.formats.plain\"><filename class=\"extension"
"\">.xml</filename></link> extension to write it in uncompressed format."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati vsebino stisnjene datoteke GZIP, jo preimenujte v ime "
"datoteke, ki se konča na <filename class=\"extension\">.gz</filename> (&eg; "
"preimenujte <filename>myfinances.kmy</filename> v <filename>myfinances.kmy."
"gz</filename>), nato uporabite <command>gunzip</command>, da datoteko "
"razpakirate in si jo ogledate. Ni vam je treba stisniti, preden jo naložite "
"v &kmymoney; naslednjič, ker &kmymoney; lahko bere tudi nestisnjene podatke. "
"Kljub temu, če jo pozneje shranite, bo znova shranjena stisnjena. Uporabite "
"pripono <link linkend=\"details.formats.plain\"><filename class=\"extension"
"\">.xml</filename></link>, da jo zapišete v nestisnjenem formatu."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "GPG-encrypted file"
msgstr "Datoteka šifrirana z GPG"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the GPG-encrypted file format is a very secure method of storing your "
"personal finance data on your storage device. When &kmymoney; has been "
"instructed through the settings dialog to store your data encrypted, it will "
"cipher the data using GPG and the key you provided before actually storing "
"it. When opening an encrypted file, you have to provide the passphrase "
"necessary to open your keyring. The encrypted file itself will be stored in "
"GPG's <emphasis>&ASCII; armored</emphasis> format."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba formata datotek, šifriranih z GPG, je zelo varen način shranjevanja "
"vaših osebnih finančnih podatkov na vašo napravo za shranjevanje. Ko "
"&kmymoney; prek pogovornega okna z nastavitvami naročimo, naj shrani vaše "
"podatke šifrirane, bo šifriral podatke z uporabo GPG in ključa, ki ste ga "
"posredovali, preden jih dejansko shrani. Ko odprete šifrirano datoteko, "
"morate vnesti geslo, ki je potrebno za odpiranje vašega obeska za ključe. "
"Sama šifrirana datoteka bo shranjena v GPG <emphasis>&ASCII; oklepnem</"
"emphasis> formatu."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using GPG encryption, GPG also compresses the file using gzip, so no "
"extra compression is necessary."
msgstr ""
"Ko uporablja šifriranje GPG, GPG tudi stisne datoteko z gzip, tako da "
"dodatno stiskanje ni potrebno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "GPG-Keys"
msgstr "Ključi GPG"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have not done so already for mail encryption, you need to generate a "
"key-pair in order to use the GPG encryption feature of &kmymoney;. Also, "
"<application>GPG</application> must be installed on your system."
msgstr ""
"Če tega še niste storili za šifriranje pošte, morate ustvariti par ključev, "
"da boste lahko uporabljali funkcijo šifriranja GPG &kmymoney;. Poleg tega "
"mora biti v vašem sistemu nameščen <application>GPG</application>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The details about how to generate a key-pair and how to take care of it are "
"beyond the scope of this document. A Mini Howto on this subject can be found "
"at <ulink url=\"https://www.gnupg.org/documentation/howtos.en.html\">https://"
"www.gnupg.org/documentation/howtos.en.html</ulink>. The web sites of most "
"&Linux; distributions also contain instructions on using GPG in that "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti o tem, kako ustvariti par ključev in kako skrbeti zanje, "
"presegajo obseg tega dokumenta. Mini navodila o tej temi najdete na <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gnupg.org/documentation/howtos.en.html\">https://www.gnupg."
"org/documentation/howtos.en. html</ulink>. Spletna mesta večine &Linux; "
"distribucije vsebujejo tudi navodila za uporabo GPG v tej distribuciji."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Setting the keys in &kmymoney;"
msgstr "Nastavitev ključev v &kmymoney;"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the encryption page of the settings dialog, there is a dropdown list "
"where you can select the key that should be used for encryption and "
"decryption. Additionally, there is a field where you can enter the key-id of "
"a key not in the listbox. You can use either the key-id, the email address "
"associated with this key, or any other valid GPG key identification as the "
"value for this field. When you enter the key-id, &kmymoney; will check its "
"validity and display a green LED icon in the dialog if a key is found."
msgstr ""
"Na strani za šifriranje v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami je spustni seznam, "
"kjer lahko izberete ključ, ki naj se uporablja za šifriranje in "
"dešifriranje. Poleg tega je na voljo polje, v katerega lahko vnesete ID "
"ključa ključa, ki ni na seznamskem polju. Kot vrednost za to polje lahko "
"uporabite ID ključa, e-poštni naslov, povezan s tem ključem, ali katero koli "
"drugo veljavno identifikacijo ključa GPG. Ko vnesete ključ-id, bo &kmymoney; "
"preveril njegovo veljavnost in prikazal zeleno ikono LED v pogovornem oknu, "
"če bo ključ najden."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make sure you have both the public and the private key for this id. If you "
"do not own the private key for the id entered, you will not be able to open "
"the file again."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da imate javni in zasebni ključ za ta določilnik. Če nimate "
"zasebnega ključa za vneseni določilnik, datoteke ne boste mogli znova "
"odpreti."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kmymoney; recovery key"
msgstr "&kmymoney; ključ za obnovo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also on this page of the settings dialog you have the choice of selecting "
"supplemental encryption with the &kmymoney; recovery key. This option is "
"available to you if that key is stored in your <application>GPG</"
"application> keyring. Selecting this option will allow you to recover your "
"data even in the case you lose your own private key. This is possible "
"because the data is not only encrypted for your own key, but also for the "
"&kmymoney; recovery key. This key is only available to selected &kmymoney; "
"developers (at the time of writing only to the author.) As of the May, 2024, "
"the recovery key is set to expire on 7 January 2025."
msgstr ""
"Tudi na tej strani pogovornega okna z nastavitvami lahko izberete dodatno "
"šifriranje s &kmymoney; ključem za obnovo. Ta možnost vam je na voljo, če je "
"ta ključ shranjen v vašem obesku ključev <application>GPG</application>. Če "
"izberete to možnost, boste lahko obnovili svoje podatke tudi v primeru, da "
"izgubite svoj zasebni ključ. To je mogoče, ker podatki niso šifrirani samo "
"za vaš ključ, ampak tudi za &kmymoney; ključ za obnovo. Ta ključ je na voljo "
"samo izbranim &kmymoney; razvijalcem (v času pisanja samo avtorju.) Od maja "
"2024 naj bi ključ za obnovo potekel 7. januarja 2025."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Under normal circumstances, you will open/save/close your file as usual. In "
"the abnormal case of loss of your key, you have the chance to contact one of "
"the developers who has access to the &kmymoney; recover key and request help "
"to recover your data. You may contact the developers via email to the "
"&kmymoney; developer mailing list at &devlist;."
msgstr ""
"V običajnih okoliščinah boste datoteko odprli/shranili/zaprli kot običajno. "
"V neobičajnem primeru izgube ključa se lahko obrnete na enega od "
"razvijalcev, ki ima dostop do &kmymoney; obnovite ključ in zahtevajte pomoč "
"pri obnovitvi podatkov. Z razvijalci se lahko obrnete po e-pošti na "
"&kmymoney; poštni seznam razvijalcev na &devlist;."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To get the recovery key, go to <ulink url=\"https://kmymoney.org/recovery."
"html\"> The KMyMoney recovery key</ulink> page of the &kmymoney; web site. "
"Copy and save the <quote>PGP PUBLIC KEY BLOCK</quote> (including the "
"<quote>BEGIN</quote> and <quote>END</quote> lines) to a text file and then "
"import it with gpg."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pridobiti ključ za obnovo, pojdite na <ulink url=\"https://"
"kmymoney.org/recovery.html\"> stran Ključ za obnovo KMyMoney</ulink> "
"storitve spletne strani &kmymoney;. Kopirajte in shranite <quote>PGP PUBLIC "
"KEY BLOCK</quote> (vključno z vrsticama <quote>BEGIN</quote> in <quote>END</"
"quote>) v besedilno datoteko in jo nato uvozite z gpg."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remember that the developer can only help recover your data file if you "
"actually do encrypt it with the recovery key, in addition to your own key."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite, da lahko razvijalec pomaga obnoviti vašo podatkovno datoteko "
"le, če jo dejansko šifrirate z obnovitvenim ključem poleg vašega lastnega "
"ključa."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Anonymous file"
msgstr "Anonimna datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This format is not intended to be used for normal data storage. It is "
"supported so that in case of a problem, you can supply the &kmymoney; "
"development team with your file without disclosing any of the confidential "
"details in your financial data. For example, it changes institution, "
"account, payee, and category names to strings such as \"I000001\" and "
"\"A000001\"; it makes similar changes to all data such as account numbers, "
"and it also randomly changes the amounts of transactions."
msgstr ""
"Ta oblika ni namenjena uporabi za običajno shranjevanje podatkov. Podprt je "
"tako, da lahko v primeru težave zagotovite &kmymoney; razvojni ekipi z vašo "
"datoteko, ne da bi razkrili zaupne podrobnosti v vaših finančnih podatkih. "
"Na primer, spremeni imena institucij, računov, prejemnikov plačil in "
"kategorij v nize, kot sta \"I000001\" in \"A000001\"; podobno spreminja vse "
"podatke, kot so številke računov, in naključno spreminja tudi zneske "
"transakcij."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If instructed by the developers, use the <guimenuitem>Save as...</"
"guimenuitem> menu item to store your data in anonymous format by selecting "
"<literal role=\"filter\">Anonymous files</literal> as the filter. This also "
"changes the file extension to <filename class=\"extension\">.anon.xml</"
"filename>."
msgstr ""
"Po navodilih razvijalcev uporabite element menija <guimenuitem>Shrani kot..."
"</guimenuitem> za shranjevanje podatkov v anonimni obliki, tako da kot "
"filter izberete <literal role=\"filter\">Anonimne datoteke</literal>. To "
"tudi spremeni pripono datoteke v <filename class=\"extension\">.anon.xml</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To verify that your problem still exists, reload this anonymized file and "
"try to duplicate your problem. If the problem is still present, send the "
"file to the developer mailing list at &devlist; for further investigation. "
"If the problem does not show ... well, I don't want to think about this "
"scenario right now."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti, ali vaša težava še vedno obstaja, znova naložite to "
"anonimizirano datoteko in poskusite podvojiti svojo težavo. Če je težava še "
"vedno prisotna, pošljite datoteko na poštni seznam razvijalcev na &devlist; "
"za nadaljnjo preiskavo. Če se težava ne pokaže ... no, zdaj ne želim "
"razmišljati o tem scenariju."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data file locations"
msgstr "Lokacije podatkovnih datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All of the above file types can be stored on a local hard drive, a removable "
"device such as a usb thumb drive, or a network location. Depending on your "
"Operating System, a remote location may need to be mapped or mounted prior "
"to use."
msgstr ""
"Vse zgornje vrste datotek je mogoče shraniti na lokalni trdi disk, "
"odstranljivo napravo, kot je na primer pogon USB, ali na omrežno lokacijo. "
"Odvisno od vašega operacijskega sistema bo morda treba oddaljeno lokacijo "
"dodeliti ali priklopiti pred uporabo."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limitation on Windows"
msgstr "Omejitev v sistemu Windows"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On &Windows;, in order to use a network or remote file location, that mapped "
"location must be mapped to a drive letter."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v &Windows; uporabiti omrežje ali lokacijo oddaljene datoteke, "
"mora biti ta preslikana lokacija preslikana v črko pogona."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup"
msgstr "Varnostna kopija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We will not attempt here to convince you that making backup copies of your "
"data is an extremely good idea; hopefully you are already convinced of that. "
"This section describes three ways to do this, and you can use any one, two, "
"or even all three of them. Note that this is about backing up a data file; "
"if you use an SQL backend to store your data, see the documentation for that "
"database system for instructions on making backups."
msgstr ""
"Tu vas ne bomo poskušali prepričati, da je izdelava varnostnih kopij vaših "
"podatkov izjemno dobra ideja; upam, da ste se že prepričali o tem. V tem "
"razdelku so opisani trije načini za to, uporabite pa lahko enega, dva ali "
"celo vse tri. Upoštevajte, da gre za varnostno kopiranje podatkovne "
"datoteke; če za shranjevanje podatkov uporabljate zaledje SQL, glejte "
"dokumentacijo za ta sistem baze podatkov za navodila o izdelavi varnostnih "
"kopij."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup file location"
msgstr "Lokacija datoteke varnostne kopije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you need a backup copy of your data to confirm some aspect of your "
"finances at a previous point in time, or to revert to an earlier state, such "
"as to undo importing a lot of data to the wrong account, it doesn't matter "
"whether the backup copy is local or stored elsewhere, such as on an attached "
"network drive. However, if you need a backup to recover from loss of data if "
"you disk drive failed, for example, it is essential that the backup is "
"<emphasis>not</emphasis> on the same drive as your primary data file. In "
"case of a larger disaster, such as a house fire, you would need a backup "
"copy stored in a fireproof safe or at a physically different location. "
"Please keep this in mind as you establish your backup strategy."
msgstr ""
"Če potrebujete varnostno kopijo svojih podatkov, da potrdite nekatere vidike "
"svojih financ v prejšnjem trenutku ali da se vrnete v prejšnje stanje, na "
"primer da razveljavite uvoz velike količine podatkov v napačen račun, ni "
"pomembno ali je varnostna kopija lokalna ali shranjena drugje, na primer na "
"priključenem omrežnem pogonu. Če pa potrebujete varnostno kopijo za "
"obnovitev po izgubi podatkov, če se na primer odpove diskovni pogon, je "
"bistveno, da varnostna kopija <emphasis>ni</emphasis> na istem pogonu kot "
"vaša primarna podatkovna datoteka. V primeru večje nesreče, kot je hišni "
"požar, bi potrebovali varnostno kopijo, shranjeno v ognjevarnem sefu ali na "
"fizično drugi lokaciji. Upoštevajte to, ko oblikujete strategijo varnostnega "
"kopiranja."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autosave"
msgstr "Samodejno shranjevanje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; has the ability to automatically save a copy of your data file at "
"regular intervals. It can also do so on closing the program, if the data has "
"changed. This behavior can be configured on the &kmymoney; <link linkend="
"\"details.settings.general.global\">configuration dialog, General section, "
"Global tab</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; ima možnost samodejnega shranjevanja kopije vaše podatkovne "
"datoteke v rednih intervalih. To lahko stori tudi ob zaprtju programa, če so "
"se podatki spremenili. To vedenje lahko konfigurirate na &kmymoney; <link "
"linkend=\"details.settings.general.global\"> pogovorno okno konfiguracije, "
"razdelek Splošno, zavihek Globalno</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "File copy"
msgstr "Kopija datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unless you are using SQL storage, your data may be compressed, and it may be "
"encrypted, but is kept in a regular file. Whenever you save your data with "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Save</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item, it writes all your data to a file, replacing the "
"previous version. The most straightforward way of backing up your data is by "
"making a copy of that file. A single copy can even have the same file name "
"if it is in a different folder than your original file, but if you are going "
"to keep multiple copies, it makes sense to include some version of the "
"current date and time in each file name. You can save these to a network "
"drive, or to a USB storage device, or even to an optical device. The primary "
"downside of this method is that you need to keep track of all the backups, "
"but it does provide the most flexibility."
msgstr ""
"Razen če uporabljate shrambo SQL, so lahko vaši podatki stisnjeni in "
"šifrirani, vendar se hranijo v navadni datoteki. Kadar koli shranite svoje "
"podatke z menijsko postavko <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Shrani</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, zapiše vse vaše "
"podatke v datoteko in nadomesti prejšnjo različico. Najpreprostejši način za "
"varnostno kopiranje podatkov je izdelava kopije te datoteke. Posamezna "
"kopija ima lahko celo isto ime datoteke, če je v drugi mapi kot izvirna "
"datoteka, vendar če boste obdržali več kopij, je smiselno, da v vsako ime "
"datoteke vključite nekaj različic trenutnega datuma in časa. Lahko jih "
"shranite na omrežni pogon, na pomnilniško napravo USB ali celo na optično "
"napravo. Glavna slaba stran te metode je, da morate spremljati vse varnostne "
"kopije, vendar zagotavlja največjo prilagodljivost."

#. Tag: title
#: details-formats.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backup command"
msgstr "Ukaz za varnostno kopiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To make things a bit easier, you can select the <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Backup</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Da bi stvari nekoliko olajšali, lahko izberete menijsko postavko "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Varnostna kopija</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-formats.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>file backup</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>varnostna kopija datoteke</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-formats.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>file backup</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>varnostno kopiranje datoteke</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> &kmymoney; will create a copy of "
"your data file, with the date (formatted as YYYY-MM-DD) appended to the "
"name. Note that this means only one backup per day can be created by this "
"method. If you have already created a backup on the same day, &kmymoney; "
"will ask if you want to replace the previous backup or cancel."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> &kmymoney; bo ustvaril kopijo vaše "
"podatkovne datoteke z datumom (oblikovan kot YYYY-MM-DD) dodanim imenu. "
"Upoštevajte, da to pomeni, da je s to metodo mogoče ustvariti samo eno "
"varnostno kopijo na dan. Če ste isti dan že ustvarili varnostno kopijo, "
"&kmymoney; vas bo vprašal, ali želite zamenjati prejšnjo varnostno kopijo "
"ali preklicati."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; will save this file to the directory specified in the "
"<guilabel>Mount Point</guilabel> field. You can either manually type the "
"full path to the directory or click <guibutton>Choose...</guibutton> and "
"navigate to it using the file browser. The directory can be on a local "
"storage device or it can be a network folder."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; bo to datoteko shranil v imenik, določen v polju <guilabel>Točka "
"priklopa</guilabel>. Lahko ročno vnesete celotno pot do imenika ali kliknete "
"<guibutton>Izberi...</guibutton> in se pomaknete do njega z brskalnikom "
"datotek. Imenik je lahko v lokalni napravi za shranjevanje ali pa je omrežna "
"mapa."

#. Tag: para
#: details-formats.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the specified directory is actually a mount point for a storage device "
"that is not always mounted, you can check the <guilabel>Mount this directory "
"before backing up</guilabel> checkbox. Do not use this for a regular network "
"file share which is always mounted."
msgstr ""
"Če je podani imenik dejansko točka priklopa za pomnilniško napravo, ki ni "
"vedno priklopljena, lahko potrdite polje <guilabel>Priklopi ta imenik pred "
"varnostnim kopiranjem</guilabel>. Tega ne uporabljajte za običajno omrežno "
"skupno rabo datotek, ki je vedno priklopljena."

