#~ "stores its information in form of an &XML; document. Depending on the "
#~ "actual format, this &XML; document will be written:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "V tem poglavju so opisani formati, v katerih &kmymoney; hrani svoje "
#~ "podatke v trajni obliki na pomnilniški napravi uporabnika. Na splošno "
#~ "&kmymoney; shrani svoje podatke v obliki &XML; dokument.a Odvisno od "
#~ "dejanskega formata, &XML; bo dokument napisan:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "as a <link linkend=\"details.formats.plain\">plain text file</link> "
#~ "encoded in UTF-8,"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "kot <link linkend=\"details.formats.plain\">datoteka z navadnim "
#~ "besedilom</link>, kodirana v UTF-8,"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "as a <link linkend=\"details.formats.compressed\">compressed file</link> "
#~ "using GZIP compression,"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "kot <link linkend=\"details.formats.compressed\">stisnjena datoteka</"
#~ "link> z uporabo stiskanja GZIP,"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "as an <link linkend=\"details.formats.encrypted\">encrypted file</link> "
#~ "using GPG encryption, or"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "kot <link linkend=\"details.formats.encrypted\">šifrirano datoteko</link> "
#~ "z uporabo šifriranja GPG ali"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "as an <link linkend=\"details.formats.anonymous\">anonymous plain text "
#~ "file</link> encoded in UTF-8 but with all your personal data scrambled."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "kot <link linkend=\"details.formats.anonymous\">anonimna datoteka z "
#~ "navadnim besedilom</link>, kodirana v UTF-8, vendar z razmetanimi vsemi "
#~ "vašimi osebnimi podatki."
